│ ### Root Cause Analysis ###                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ -------------------- BEGIN --------------------                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ The assertion failure in `computeBestVF` is caused by a mismatch between the VPlan-based and legacy cost models. The `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` function, which is supposed to identify if the VPlan │
│ introduces simplifications, is returning false incorrectly. This is likely due to incomplete population of the `SkipCostComputation` set in `CostCtx` by `precomputeCosts`. Adding debug logging and ensuring     │
│ proper population of `SkipCostComputation` will help identify and fix the issue.                                                                                                                                  │
│ --------------------  END  --------------------                                                                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ ## Suspected Code Locations ##                                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                   │
